"```sql\nSELECT Country.name\nFROM Player\nJOIN Match ON Player.player_api_id = Match.home_player_1 OR Player.player_api_id = Match.away_player_1\nJOIN League ON Match.league_id = League.id\nJOIN Country ON League.country_id = Country.id\nGROUP BY Country.name\nORDER BY AVG(Player.weight) DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query joins the necessary tables to find the country with the heaviest average player weights. It groups the results by country and orders them by the average weight in descending order, selecting the top result."